description: London, UK In Double-Decker Tour, you get on a double-decker bus, which is commonly used throughout the United Kingdom and is a national symbol of England. The tour will take you throughout the city of London, viewing world-famous and popular tourist locations such as the Palace of Westminster, Tower Bridge, etc.. The video can also be enjoyed at night-time with buildings lit up. The audio in this video is in English.
